img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746040/extras/c57ae2e2a4197349f4e01e41fefa2aa8.poster.avif?t=1663883069\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746040/extras/c57ae2e2a4197349f4e01e41fefa2aa8.webm?t=1663883069\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746040/extras/c57ae2e2a4197349f4e01e41fefa2aa8.mp4?t=1663883069\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Brutal Bosses</strong><br>Put your skills to the test against brutal bosses. Choose your strategy and your build carefully to overcome them.",
